Nigerian singer Toby Grey is on a fast rise in the music industry as she is not relenting in her efforts. The songbird has followed up her latest single “Show Glass” with a perfect remix and for this she signed the help of Terry Apala and Chinko Ekun. Read More: NEAs 2016:  ‘Battle royale’ for  Nigerian artistes There was the commendable use of Yoruba language as well as pidgin to deliver the prayer-filled lyrics of the song. The song was produced by rising music producer Tyemmy. Listen to the song HERE.